	Our CDs are the perfect toolkit to pursue and assist a chosen therapy, energy or pastime. The music has been crafted to produce an ambience that allows the mind freedom for healing, visualisation and relaxation with consistent mood and texture. This wonderful CD has a blend of music ideally suited to Reiki healing, massage and relaxation. An ancient from of Tibetan healing, Reiki was brought back to Japan by Doctor Mikao Usui in the late 19<sup>th</sup> century after many years of searching in all areas of Buddhist faith. Working in a holistic manner healing mind, body and spirit, Reiki can bring about many positive changes in the individual at all levels.&nbsp;</p>
